Description:
Yaha tum GitOps introduce karte ho with ArgoCD. Terraform se infra banta hai, Jenkins image build karta hai, aur ArgoCD + Helm deploy karta hai.

🛠 Tools Used:

Terraform

Jenkins

Docker

Kubernetes

Helm

ArgoCD (GitOps)

🏗 Architecture:
Terraform → AWS Infra + K8s Cluster
Jenkins → Docker Build + Push → Git (Helm chart update)
